2:05.000Z","msg":"無話靠唔靠，本來一個國家正常都會歡迎各國技術人才，但係中國咁賤格一味偷人科技，人地只好趕你走，中國人變成過街老鼠，無外國請"},{"pid":"afbb3e6bc954c3b1c8079a436db5018572dbfe9c","tid":951060,"uid":134437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:17:57.000Z","msg":"1. 這家工廠的總部就在香港, 算不得純正印度公司<br />\n2. 香港派出的培訓人員59名 (估計全是大陸護照), 拿的是商務考察簽證, 據說是做培訓示範工作. 但很可能搶了印度人飯碗, 被告發.<br />\n3. 印度移民局外國人管理處發現後, 要求這些人離境, 共匪就升級為政治陰謀, 又準備辱華了."},{"pid":"f9f573d1470c183c79e297d9dedff5bbceeda4c0","tid":951060,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:21:58.000Z","msg":"要拉印度人了"},{"pid":"68a26957e1787ca8e1c66fa3ca772d4a9a669acb","tid":951060,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eed4fda9d68f4269bd9951ce6b7c04383c53893","tid":951060,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1bdcfd0f89949efee5f704654531c1f88b6802","tid":951060,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a91119f73863af8f2c941a3120f3ef7a68a3538","tid":951060,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T04:42:32.000Z","msg":"點解印度科技咁堅都要靠中國人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"平 賤價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"印度唔平咩？唔多精通英文人材咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"首先唔係精通英文，佢地啲口音真係好衰，其次做野好慢"},{"pid":"f451408b906248d535001541e21c720ecf250a95","tid":951060,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a26957e1787ca8e1c66fa3ca772d4a9a669acb","tid":951060,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eed4fda9d68f4269bd9951ce6b7c04383c53893","tid":951060,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b1bdcfd0f89949efee5f704654531c1f88b6802","tid":951060,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"平 賤價"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"印度唔平咩？唔多精通英文人材咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"首先唔係精通英文，佢地啲口音真係好衰，